methods.name: getRotationY
methods.notes: Returns the rotation about the Y axis, in radians.

methods.name: getRotationZ
methods.notes: Returns the rotation about the Z axis, in radians.

methods.name: ToEulerAngles
methods.notes:
Convert the supplied Quaternion to Euler angles.
  Source: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conversion_between_quaternions_and_Euler_angles

methods.name: ToQuaternion
methods.notes:
Convert the supplied Euler angles to a Quaternion.
  Source: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conversion_between_quaternions_and_Euler_angles

methods.name: transform
methods.notes:
Applies the supplied quaternion to transform the supplied in_vector,
  stores the result in the supplied out_result.

methods.name: Add
methods.notes: Add the supplied character to the visible render list.

methods.name: ContainsChar
methods.notes: Returns TRUE if the character is currently in the visible render list, and has not been flagged for removal.
